This paper deals with approximation algorithms for a combinatorial optimization problem involving clustering and facility location. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). Additionally, the paper proposes an algorithm that uses machine learning techniques, which makes it relevant to the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
